* [[德州穴龜|德州穴龜]] (''Gopherus berlandieri'' <small>([[Louis_Agassiz|Agassiz]], 1857)</small>）
* [[黃緣穴龜|黃緣穴龜]] (''Gopherus flavomarginatus'' (<small>[[John_M._Legler|Legler]], 1959))</small>
*[[索諾蘭穴龟|索諾蘭穴龟]] (''Gopherus morafkai'' (<small>Murphy et al., 2011))</small><ref name="usgs.gov"/>
